title: Asphalt | Nyjah Huston Signature Collection
description:
AYC is proud to announce its first ever signature collection, created in conjunction with team member and skateboarding icon Nyjah Huston. Designed by AYC and Nyjah, the new collection draws inspiration from the passion, dedication, and personal style of skateboarding’s most talked-about figure. With custom tiger-camo and floral patterns and featuring tees, raglans, and hats, the collection brings confident, assertive concepts together with AYC’s clean, streetwear aesthetic.

The AYC Nyjah Huston Collection will be available exclusively at Tilly’s and Tillys.com on 8/26. 

Filmed By: Mike Manzoori
Music By: Nice Beats
